     C           @@@       TAG
     C                     Z-ADDX         XXX     50
     C                     MOVEA'0'       *IN,10
     C                     DO   CNT       I
     C           WBARL     MULT I         MAX     50
     C           X         DO   CDCIBI    J
     C           HAK,J     IFLT MAX
     C                     ADD  WBARL     HAK,J
     C                     SUB  1         WBLSRY
     C                     SUB  WBSRYO    WHSRYO
     C                     Z-ADDJ         XXX
